-- Desktop look --
	+ Go to desktop
	+ Right click on every panel -> (bin) Remove panel
	+ Right click on desktop -> Add Panel -> Default Panel
	+ Right click on panel -> Edit Panel
		+ Make height smaller
		+ Put it on the upper screen edge
		+ Remove "Minimize all Windows"
		+ Remove "Pager"
		+ Remove "Task Manager"
	Right click on panel -> Add widgets
		+ Add "Icons only task manager" after the app dashboard
	+ Right click on Application Launcher on Panel -> Show Alternatives -> Application Dashboard
	+ Right click on Application Launcher on Panel -> Configure Application Dashboard
		+ Show categories
			+ Recent application(OFF)
			+ Recent documents(OFF)
		+ Expand search to bookmarks, files and emails(OFF)
	+ Right click on Lock/Logout -> Configure Lock/Logout
		+ Show actions -> Lock(OFF)
	+ Right click on System tray -> Configure System tray
		+ Media Player(Disabled)
		+ Updates(Always hidden)
		+ Device Notifier(Disabled)
		+ Keyboard Indicator(Disabled)
		+ Networks(Always shown)
		+ Printers(Disabled)
		+ Clipboard(Disabled)
		+ Night Color Color(Disabled)
		+ Vaults(Disabled)
	+ Right click on desktop -> Configure Desktop -> Wallpaper -> Change
	
-- Configure system --
	+ Open system settings
	+ Appearance
		+ Global theme -> Breeze Dark
	+ Workspace
		+ Workspace
			+ General Behavior -> Animation Speed(Instant)
			+ Desktop Effects -> Screen Edge(OFF)
			+ Screen Locking -> Appearance -> Change wallpaper
		+ Shortcuts
			+ Kwin
				+ Switch to Desktop num(meta + f(num))
				+ Windows to Desktop num(ctrl + f(num))
				+ Show Desktop Grid(meta + esc)
			+ Add(+) - terminator(ctrl + alt + t)
	+ Personalization
		+ Account Details -> Kde Wallet -> Enable the KDE wallet subsystem(OFF)
		+ Applications -> Set default
	+ Hardware
		+ Power Management -> Settings are device specific
		
-- Extra --
 + Remove bloatware
	+ (terminal) sudo apt remove skanlite okular vlc kate kcalc
	+ (terminal) sudo apt remove kdeconnect #optional 
  + (terminal) sudo apt autoremove
